(Cloud-Optimised) GeoTIFFs onto a target grid, following the \code{gdalwarp}
argument interface (\code{t_srs} / \code{te} / \code{tr} / \code{ts} / \code{r} / \code{bands} / \code{cl_arg})
}
}

